      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"blinded by short-sighted fears\" bit sounds a little harsh don't u think? Is it really just fear, or are people actually worried about their jobs and the power grid? It seems like a pretty big deal for the families in those coal towns.",
